<paragraph blockId="0.[1236,2116,603,762]" pageId="0" pageNumber="272">• Medium-sized and arboreal with extensive patagium for gliding; large forward-facing eyes, small ears, slender limbs, and light musculature.</paragraph>
<caption ID-DOI="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6628159" ID-Zenodo-Dep="6628159" box="[1236,1424,724,762]" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6628159/files/figure.png" inLine="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="272" startId="0.[1236,1248,724,762]" targetBox="[1429,1769,769,958]" targetPageId="0">
<paragraph blockId="0.[1236,2116,603,762]" box="[1236,1424,724,762]" pageId="0" pageNumber="272">e 50-70 cm.</paragraph>
</caption>
<paragraph blockId="0.[1236,2115,977,1176]" box="[1236,1607,977,1010]" pageId="0" pageNumber="272">
<caption ID-DOI="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6628161" ID-Zenodo-Dep="6628161" box="[1236,1603,977,1010]" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6628161/files/figure.png" inLine="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="272" startId="0.[1236,1248,977,1010]" targetBox="[221,1166,609,1231]" targetPageId="0">• Indo-Malayan Region</caption>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="0.[1236,2115,977,1176]" pageId="0" pageNumber="272">• Primary and secondary tropical rainforests and forest plantations, with trees of sufficient height for gliding.</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="0.[1236,2115,977,1176]" box="[1236,1672,1101,1134]" pageId="0" pageNumber="272">• 2 genera, 2 species, b taxa,</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="0.[1236,2115,977,1176]" box="[1236,2005,1147,1176]" pageId="0" pageNumber="272">• No species threatened; none Extinct since 1600.</paragraph>
